<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="limit-v">limit <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'lɪmɪt/    美 /'lɪmɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>限制；限定：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A lack of formal education will limit your job opportunities. 
缺乏正规教育会限制你的就业机会。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="limit-to">limit … to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>将…限制在 (某范围内)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I believe teaching should not be limited to the classroom.
我认为教学不应该局限于教室之内。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I limit myself to two cups of coffee a day. 
我只允许自己一天喝两杯咖啡。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>limitation  /ˌlɪmɪ'teɪʃn/ n [U] &amp; [C] <br />
limiting /'lɪmɪtɪŋ/ adj <br />
limitless /'lɪmɪtləs/ adj   </p>
<h2 id="_4">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Knowledge and learning are important if we want to be successful, but they may also <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (限制) our thinking.  （2011 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. limit  </p></div>